SELECT "B"."hihokenshaNo" AS "taishoHihokenshaNo" ,"B"."seiriNo" AS "seiriNo" ,"B"."rirekiNo" AS "rirekiNo" ,"B"."jikoFutan_KeisanYM" AS "jikoFutanKeisanYM" ,"B"."taishoNendo" AS "taishoNendo" ,"B"."hokenshaNo" AS "hokenshaNo" ,"B"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" AS "shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" ,"B"."taishoKeisanKaishiYMD" AS "taishoKeisanKaishiYMD" ,"B"."taishoKeisanShuryoYMD" AS "taishoKeisanShuryoYMD" ,"B"."kanyuKaishiYMD" AS "kanyuKaishiYMD" ,"B"."kanyuShuryoYMD" AS "kanyuShuryoYMD" ,"B"."shinseiYMD" AS "shinseiYMD" ,"B"."kokuho_HihokenshaShoKigo" AS "kokuho_HihokenshaShoKigo" ,"V1001"."hihokenshaNo" AS "daichoHihokenshaNo" ,(CASE "V1001"."koikinaiJushochiTokureiFlag" WHEN '1' THEN "V1001"."koikinaiTokureiSochimotoShichosonCode" ELSE "V1001"."shichosonCode" END) AS "shichosonCode" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."kanaMeisho" AS "kanaMeisho" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."meisho" AS "meisho" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."seinengappiYMD" AS "seinengappiYMD" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."seibetsuCode" AS "seibetsuCode" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."yubinNo" AS "yubinNo" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."choikiCode" AS "choikiCode" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."gyoseikuCode" AS "gyoseikuCode" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."juminShubetsuCode" AS "juminShubetsuCode" ,"ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode" AS "shikibetsuCode" FROM (SELECT "dbt3068"."hihokenshaNo" ,"dbt3068"."taishoNendo" ,"dbt3068"."hokenshaNo" ,"dbt3068"."seiriNo" ,MAX("dbt3068"."rirekiNo") AS "rirekiNo" FROM rgdb."DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho" AS "dbt3068" WHERE "dbt3068"."isDeleted"= False GROUP BY "dbt3068"."hihokenshaNo" ,"dbt3068"."taishoNendo" ,"dbt3068"."hokenshaNo" ,"dbt3068"."seiriNo" ) AS "K" INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho" AS "B" ON "K"."hihokenshaNo" = "B"."hihokenshaNo" AND "K"."taishoNendo" = "B"."taishoNendo" AND "K"."hokenshaNo" = "B"."hokenshaNo" AND "K"."seiriNo" = "B"."seiriNo" AND "K"."rirekiNo" = "B"."rirekiNo" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" AS "V1001" ON "V1001"."hihokenshaNo"= "B"."hihokenshaNo" LEFT JOIN
AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode"="V1001"."shikibetsuCode" WHERE "B"."isDeleted" =False AND #{申請対象日開始} <= "B"."shinseiYMD" AND "B"."shinseiYMD"<=#{申請対象日終了} AND "B"."shinseiJokyoKubun" = '2' AND ("B"."shikyuShinseiKubun" ='1' or "B"."shikyuShinseiKubun"='2') AND (("B"."jikoFutan_KeisanYM"= '' OR "B"."jikoFutan_KeisanYM" is NULL) OR ("B"."jikoFutan_KeisanYM" <>'' AND "B"."jikoFutan_KeisanYM" is NOT NULL AND "B"."saiKeisanKubun" = '1')) ORDER BY "B"."hihokenshaNo" ASC
